Usage: setHierFlowMode [-help] [-reset] [-budgets {accurate|preliminary|none}]

-help                                    # Prints out the command usage
-reset                                   # Resets all or specified options to default value
-budgets {accurate|preliminary|none}     # This will set budgeting mode options
                                         # via setBudgetingMode command for
                                         # accurate or preliminary budgeting
                                         # whichever is specified. It has lower
                                         # precedence than other user specified
                                         # budgeting mode settings.
                                         # (enums={accurate preliminary none}, default=none)